{
  "text": "The motivation for this work is thus to ͑1͒ demonstrate the use of a very compact, high-reflectivity mirror as the feedback element for a DBR semiconductor laser and ͑2͒ confirm the previous transmission measurements [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] in re-flection. The cavity layout is shown in Fig. 1͑a͒ , and the actual device in Fig. 2 .",
  "correct_citation": {
